text: The Sunshine Underground is the third studio album by British indie band The Sunshine Underground, whose self-titled album marked a shift in genre from indie-rock in their previous two albums to a more electronic sound reminiscent of 80s synthpop. ==Track listing== # Start – 5:53 # Finally We Arrive – 4:08 # Nothing To Fear – 3:53 # Don't Stop – 5:06 # Battles – 7:07 # Nightlife – 4:21 # The Same Old Ghosts – 6:25 # It Is Only You – 6:07 # Turn It On – 3:29 # Here Comes The Storm – 4:55 ==References== Category:2014 albums Category:The Sunshine Underground albums
title: The Sunshine Underground (album)
